# Layered Architecture

Use the project layers consistently:

- `api` handles requests only.
- `services` contain business logic.
- `repositories` contain data access only.
- `models` define domain models.
- `schemas` define DTOs.
- `core` contains configuration and shared utilities.

Never mix responsibilities between layers.
